						"displayName": "David van de Meer",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "this is a SDK design oversight problem, not a Android device issue. \r\n\r\n`tintColor` and `trackTintColor ` should set the Progressbar Color\r\n`color` should set the text color\r\n\r\nthe sdk module only accounts for color as seen here and uses that to set the progress bar color as well\r\nhttps://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/blob/master/android/modules/ui/src/java/ti/modules/titanium/ui/widget/TiUIProgressBar.java#L67 ",
